    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>WHO WILL HELP THE BLACK MAN?</hl1>
      </hedline>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Because whitey ain't going to give us a break." I would like to thank Ken Hamblin for sharing that insightful remark.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>Because whitey ain't going to give us a break." I would like to thank Ken Hamblin for sharing that insightful remark.</p>
        <p>I am "whitey" and I will give a break to anybody who has earned it. I do not judge others based upon the color of their skin. I expect the same courtesy. If we do not have that as a common ground, we have nothing. STEPHEN BERNSTEIN New York</p>
      </block>
